cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.LG 

This paper deals with image segmentation, specifically for sky/cloud images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves evaluation using principal component analysis (PCA) and fuzzy clustering, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Additionally, the paper deals with color spaces and components, which are relevant to graphics (cs.GR) and machine learning (cs.LG) research.
